    <step order="2">Identify target solution: either the existing solution that hosts `sprk_aichatcontextmap` OR the new `SpaarkeActionEngine` solution. Document decision in `notes/decisions/aichatcontextmap-extension-targeting.md`. **Prefer**: keep the entity in its current solution; layer the extension via solution segmentation if Dataverse supports it for this entity.</step>
